axisLabel.color.desc:
 Color of axis label is set to be [axisLine.lineStyle.color][0] by default. Callback function is supported, in the following format: 

    (val: string) => Color


Parameter is the text of label, and return value is the color. See the following example: 

    textStyle: {
        color: function (value, index) {
            return value >= 0 ? 'green' : 'red';
        }
    }




